      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "## What's Changed in v1.1.0\r\n\r\nThis release focuses on strengthening the project's codebase through improved type safety and refined UI styling, while expanding our documentation to help users better integrate companion tools.\r\n\r\n### Highlights\r\n\r\n* **Enhanced Stability**: Comprehensive refactoring of core systems to improve type safety and reduce potential runtime errors.\r\n* **Refined Interface**: Cleaned up CSS architecture for a more consistent and maintainable UI.\r\n* **Expanded Documentation**: New guides for installing via BRAT and utilizing companion tools like `vce2flashquiz`.\r\n\r\n### What's Changed\r\n\r\n* **Codebase Improvements**: Enhanced type safety across the core module, including better handling of JSON data and module imports, leading to a more robust and predictable application.\r\n* **UI Refinement**: Scoped CSS selectors to prevent style conflicts and removed unnecessary overrides for a cleaner visual foundation.\r\n* **Documentation Updates**: Added detailed installation instructions for the BRAT plugin and a new \"Companion Tools\" section to help users convert and manage their quiz data more effectively.\r\n\r\n### Full Changelog\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/nazdridoy/obsidian-cbt-exam/compare/1.5.2...1.5.3",
